PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FHere he wrote down his sickening
OL,7,Ffantasies, admitting he hated women
OL,8,Fand girls and openly plotting to kill
OL,9,Fhis mum. When concerns about his
OL,10,Fbehaviour were raised he would get
OL,11,Fbanned but then would start again
OL,12,Funder a new pseudonym.
OL,14,FThis was a teen obsessed with U.S.
OL,15,Fcrime drama Dexter and the film
OL,16,FAmerican Psycho. His chat history
OL,17,Freleased by North Wales Police was
OL,18,Fchilling.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FHe told one member of the site "I do
OL,7,Fhate girls. Are you OK with that?
OL,8,FGirls/ Women. I also don't trust them".
OL,10,FHe then went on to talk openly about
OL,11,Fmurdering his mother. He changed his
OL,12,Fuser name to 'Tonights the night' and
OL,13,Ftyped 'So you can see how I feel after
OL,14,Fkilling her right?'
OL,16,FRoberts was diagnosed with Autism and
OL,17,FADHD, he had previously run away from
OL,18,Fhome and spent time in a hotel for
OL,19,Fhomeless people in Rhyl.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FPsychiatric evidence submitted to Mold
OL,7,FCrown Court confirmed his diagnoses
OL,8,Fand also Roberts' discussions of
OL,9,Fchildhood trauma.
OL,11,FHis mother Angela Shellis had reached
OL,12,Fout to various people and
OL,13,Forganisations for help.
OL,15,FThe full details of what happened
OL,16,Fleading up to the murder aren't fully
OL,17,Fknown as Roberts plead guilty to his
OL,18,Fcrime and so there was no trial.
OL,19,FHowever, we know 45-year-old Angela
OL,20,FShellis was a dedicated parent.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FShe moved back to north Wales from
OL,7,FBedfordshire and although a qualified
OL,8,Fteacher she chose to work as a
OL,9,Fteaching assistant to have more time
OL,10,Favailable for her adult children.
OL,12,FShe advocated for Tristan as he
OL,13,Fstruggled with his mental health but
OL,14,Fhe plotted her death and murdered her
OL,15,Finside a Denbighshire nature reserve.
OL,17,FAt 8.30am on Friday 24 October, North
OL,18,FWales Police took a call to say that a
OL,19,Fbody had been found. It was in the
OL,20,FMorfa woodland.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FNearby lay a crutch. Police didn't
OL,7,Fknow if it was significant - it would
OL,8,Fbe.
OL,10,FThere was a trail of blood along a
OL,11,Fgravel path, discarded gloves
OL,12,Fsaturated in blood and a balaclava.
OL,13,FDetectives had no idea who the victims
OL,14,Fwas and it would be a number of hours
OL,15,Fbefore they identified Angela Shellis.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FThe pieces only came together when
OL,7,Fmurder squad detectives were told a
OL,8,Fcall had come in to the front desk
OL,9,Ffrom concerned family members who
OL,10,Fcouldn't reach their relative. They
OL,11,Foffered a key piece of information -
OL,12,Fthe missing woman used a crutch to
OL,13,Fwalk after damaging her knee.
OL,15,FPolice rushed to Coniston Drive where
OL,16,FTristan Roberts answered the door and
OL,17,Fwas arrested. Inside the semi-detached
OL,18,Fhome they discovered a murder kit he
OL,19,Fhad put together.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FAmong the items found were a hammer
OL,7,Fand a blood stained water bottle.
OL,8,FAngela's mobile phone was also found
OL,9,Fin the bottom of the wardrobe. Tristan
OL,10,Fhad been using it to respond as if he
OL,11,Fwas her to concerned relatives.
OL,13,FDetectives pieced together that he
OL,14,Fattacked his mum inside her own home.
OL,15,FBruises and strangulation marks were
OL,16,Ffound on her body.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
