FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FHe recorded their conversation on that
OL,7,Ffateful night on a dictaphone - it
OL,8,Fgave police all the evidence they
OL,9,Fneeded, a verbal account outlining how
OL,10,Fhe attacked Angela and eventually
OL,11,Fkilled her.
OL,13,FAfter attacking her on that October
OL,14,Fnight, the teen tried to get her to go
OL,15,Fto sleep. When she refused, he
OL,16,Fpersuaded her to leave their house to
OL,17,Fget medical help.
OL,19,FRing doorbell footage captures them
OL,20,Fleaving.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FThey are then picked up again on
OL,7,Fcameras as they crossed the Sandy Lane
OL,8,Frailway crossing. Roberts can be seen
OL,9,Fwith a rucksack - this is carrying the
OL,10,Fmurder weapon and the dictaphone is
OL,11,Fstill recording.
OL,13,FThe crossing leads straight to the
OL,14,Fnature reserve. It was pitch black.
OL,15,FThe area was deserted - there would
OL,16,Fhave been no one around to witness him
OL,17,Fattack and murder his defenceless
OL,18,Fmother.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,FHe hits her over the head several
OL,7,Ftimes with a hammer. He leaves
OL,8,FAngela's body and walks back home.
OL,9,FCCTV catches him crossing the railway
OL,10,Fline - this time alone.
OL,12,FWhen police arrive to arrest him he is
OL,13,Fcompliant but refuses to answer any
OL,14,Fquestions. Answering "No comment"
OL,15,Fduring the interview.
OL,17,FAndrew Slight of the Crown Prosecution
OL,18,FService said: "The level of planning
OL,19,FTristan Roberts did ahead of
OL,20,Fcommitting this shocking crime was
OL,21,Felaborate and calculated.
OL,26,@zD@OOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774552271
OL,3,CThe tragic story of the loving mother
OL,4,Cbrutally murdered by her own son
OL,6,F"His mother's final moments must have
OL,7,Fbeen terrifying, yet he showed no
OL,8,Fconcern or remorse for his actions.
OL,10,F"The strong evidence presented by the
OL,11,FCrown Prosecution Service painted a
OL,12,Fclear picture, showing Roberts'
OL,13,Fintentions, resulting in his guilty
OL,14,Fplea.
OL,16,F"Although this case has concluded, our
OL,17,Fthoughts remain with the family and
OL,18,Ffriends who still feel the terrible
OL,19,Floss of Angela."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
